column9:
Dear sirs,
We are a Polish textile design company with branches in Minsk, Belarus and Moscow, Russia. We are very interested to work with your wonderful collection. Would you be interested? Please, kindly tell us what the terms and conditions, based on which we can get your hangers. We are also interested to buy a particular fabric: Design: Columbia col. 000, 11m. Would you be so kind to tell us the price and shipping time to Warsaw.
Thank you.
Best Regards,
Daniela Shrivastava
